{"article_id":"Qky43HgfcEo8gWBd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A flawed response to the first case of Ebola in the United States has led to a second nurse being diagnosed .","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"Wednesday morning , the Texas Department of State Health Services confirmed the diagnosis of a second nurse","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that helped care for Liberian Ebola patient Thomas Eric Duncan at Dallas 's Texas Health Presbyterian Hospital before his death last week .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"A nurse","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"named Nina Pham","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"was diagnosed over the weekend","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"and is now being treated .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"The announcement came","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"as the director of the federal Centers for Disease Control and Prevention , Tom Frieden , acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that his agency was too slow","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"in responding to the situation at the Dallas hospital .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Failure","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to follow protocol","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"was the cause for the new cases ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"health officials have said ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"but a nurses ' union , Nurses United , cited unnamed nurses","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"who claimed","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"protocols changed constantly","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"as the hospital tried to figure out what to do with Mr. Duncan .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The union also claimed","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that needless numbers of people were exposed to Duncan","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"as soiled bedclothes and other detritus piled up in his room .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"The flawed response isn ' t surprising in many ways ,","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"given that this has been the US health care system ' s first test with the illness .","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"The failure","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to completely contain the virus","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"has forced the CDC to create a new \" Ebola response unit \"","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to help other hospitals prepare","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"as the agency acknowledges","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"the US may see more cases .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"One part of that plan is to limit exposure of victims to fewer nurses and doctors .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"`` Ebola is unfamiliar , ''","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Dr. Frieden said ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"stressing","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"that getting the response `` right is really , really important . ''","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"`` I wish","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"we had put a team like this on the ground the day","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"the patient","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"- the first patient -","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"was diagnosed , ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"`` That might have prevented '' the additional diagnoses .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Frieden has vowed","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"that the agency is prepared to stop the illness \" in its tracks \"","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"but acknowledged on Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"that fear of the illness among health care workers is a problematic aspect of the response .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"Public health officials reiterated Tuesday","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"that the risk","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"of the public contracting Ebola","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"is \" exceedingly low \"","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"as it does not spread through the air .","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"The illness has become a global crisis after the deaths of 4,500 people in West Africa in the largest outbreak of its kind .","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"The World Health Organization said Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"that the survival rate has fallen from 50 percent to 30 percent ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"and it predicts as many as 10,000 new cases by Christmas .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"In recent weeks , new cases have been diagnosed in the US and Europe .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"Seven patients have been treated","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"or are being treated in the US ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"and so far Mr. Duncan is the only one","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"to die .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":129,"left":110,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":88,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":86,"right":87,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":75,"right":85,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":0,"right":74,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":70,"right":73,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":66,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":68,"left":67,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":7,"right":72,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":8,"right":71,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":71,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":78,"right":84,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":76,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":76,"left":11,"right":12,"relati